            <span style="color:#C89B3C;margin-right:8px;">&#9670;</span> Revisar VODs com anotações em timestamps
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:5px 0;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#bcc4cf;">
            <span style="color:#C89B3C;margin-right:8px;">&#9670;</span> Fazer scouting de talentos e acompanhar prospects
